name: Investab corporate website
description:
Investab is a pure multi-purpose PSD theme and Figma

suitable for any area of your business. It is loaded with layers and very easy to edit. You can edit and customize it for any of your needs, more than 25 pages that you need

Features

- 24 full layer Adobe Photoshop .PSD and Figma files

- All pages are adapted and more than 24 pages are adapted

- Boxed and wide style

- Designed with responsiveness in mind

- Clean, modern design

- Well organized layers make it very easy to update

- All fonts used in templates are available in google font
